stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Ready
  Ready --> Thinking: "Build context for this round"
  Thinking --> Acting: "Model returns tool intent"
  Thinking --> Finished: "model returns final"
  Acting --> Observing: "Tool execution completed"
  Observing --> Ready: "observation writes back to state"
  Thinking --> Stopped: "Overrun/Budget"
  Acting --> Stopped: "Interrupt/Permission Denied/Tool Fatal Error"
  Stopped --> [*]
  Finished --> [*]
